Class org.apache.metamodel.data.DefaultRow extends AbstractRow implements Serializable

serialVersionUID: 1L

Serialization Methods

readObject

private void readObject(ObjectInputStream stream)
                 throws Exception
Method invoked by the Java serialization framework while deserializing Row instances. Since previous versions of MetaModel did not use a DataSetHeader, but had a reference to a List, this deserialization is particularly tricky. We check if the items variable is there, and if it is, we convert it to a header instead.

Throws:
Exception
